channel.title: Submitting Server (NO.IP) Problem
channel.description:
Hey, im elite, the owner of [Url=http://Elite-Scape]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,152756.msg1440416.html#msg1440416[/url]. And im having problems with no ip. When i try to submit it to this list [url=clickiehttp://www.flashspace.us/serverstatus.php?action=register[/url]. It says server is offline. When infact (While my HAM is still running) People are on it. Here is my NO.IP Info
elite-scape.no-ip.org 208.191.58.202 [IP]
When i submit, i type
Elite-Scape 208.191.58.202 43694
When i enter, it say. "The server elite-scape.no-ip.org is offline, it must be online before you can register it here."
What am i doig wrong? & How do imake it online?

item.title: Submitting Server (NO.IP) Problem
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Basically you can use your Hamachi IP-Address and convert it to “No-Ip”. Although, on the server status page, it reuests that you do not try to enter a Hamachi server. It is saying it is down because Hamachi was detected. Furthermore, if you have a Hamachi server, you may not enter it on the server status page.

Also, please read the rules of this board. It clearly states that you are not allowed to “Bump” or double post your thread; please review them right now.

–Tico135–
